user.biography:
Kate E. Richards

21+ only, k?
There's a book now! 👇

node.text:
Since Corn loves fountains so damned much, @jojotastic gifted us with this @lampsplus #fountain knowing full well that I’d get crafty and add a little extra color to it. And that Corn would spend a lot of time standing on it.
-
So here’s a glimpse at what DIY-ing looks like at our house. With #chickens. And #cocktails. And also #dogs named Rooster.
-
And now Corn has a new fountain to gaze at. Thanks @jojotastic & @lampsplus !!!
#drinkingwithchickens #diywithchickens .
.
.
.
#diyhomedecor #DIY #chickenlife #happyhour #weekendwarriors #craftsandcocktails #craftlife #addsomecolor #putachickenonit #makersgonnamake #pennytile

node.text:
Can someone please explain to me why I can’t quit putting jaunty headwear on my chickens? WHY DOES MY BRAIN WANT MY TINY CHICKEN TO BE WEARING A TINY APPLE HELMET.
SEND HELP.
jk I don’t really want to be helped.
-
I digress.
My point….what was it. Oh yes. It’s kinda fall and it’s kinda still summer, so here’s a refreshing little cocktail that awkwardly straddles both seasons: The Mulled Maple Apple Daiquiri. Let’s do #apples and mulling spices but let’s put them in a summery #daiquiri because we do what we want. Link to recipe in profile.
-
Back to the apple helmet. I painstakingly carved it from a real, tiny apple (with a tiny spoon, ok?), custom-contured for Parsnip’s tiny nog. She was unappreciative. #madhatter
#drinkingwithchickens
.

We've been hard at work behind the scenes putting together that house and garden tour I've been promising for ELEVENTY YEARS. I'll be unloading all that in the coming weeks, but I thought I'd start with a little swipey-swipey before and after action of the front of the house, plus some background on our 113-year-old home. To call it a fixer-upper is a hilarious understatement. Let's just say there were many, many reasons why our entire front and back gardens have hundreds of upcycled wine bottles as landscape edging. 😆 But such is #renovationlife, right? If you've been following me for a bit, then you might have picked up on the fact that I'm obsessed with @goodcleanwine. I hoard my shipments--HOARD them--in fact, to put it in universally relatable #chicken terms, I'm downright broody hen about them (flattening my body over the bottles and hissing at anyone who tries to take one).
BUT BIG NEWS: these gorgeous, headache-free wines are finally available by subscription (and you get 10% off if you subscribe), so now I can be slightly less cranky about sharing cuz my hoard is being replenished by the magic of e-commerce. 
-
Side note: if you let your #chicken perch on your @goodcleanwine bottles, they will be slightly less clean. Do as I say, not as I do. 
-
Side-side note: this is not an ad. I'm just a huge fan and also wanted everyone to look at my cute chicken. Ok, byeeeeee.

node.text:
Celebrating National Mutt Day by hanging out with a few of our #mutts and drinking a few Salty Dogs. And, since these two #chickens are ALSO mutts, we ALSO did a variation called a Salty Hen (basically a Salty Dog with egg white and a bit of honey syrup added to it), because……I’m me.
-
To make it:
Shake 3 oz fresh grapefruit juice, 1.5 oz #vodka, .5 oz honey syrup (1:1 honey and hot water mixed thoroughly then cooled), 1 medium egg white, and a pinch of salt in a cocktail shaker with ice and shake until chilled and frothy. Strain into a salt-rimmed coupe.
-
If you want a Salty Dog, omit the egg and the syrup (although I always put a touch of syrup in mine) and serve on the rocks.
-
Also of note: one of these mutts is molting and is legit a Salty Hen.
#drinkingwithchickens
.
.
.
.
#happyhourathome #drinkingwithdogs #porchdrinks #porchsitting #chickenlife #doglife #backdeck #vodkadrinks #saltydog #creaturecomfystyle #muttlife #cocktailhour #cocktaillife #ilovemutts

node.text:
#AD | We have a definite tendency to put our poultry up on a pedestal around here. Figuratively. And literally: cuz it keeps them outta the #cocktails. But yes very much figuratively, too, okay?! But also? This Scarlet Fruit Tequila Sour that combines both @exoticotequila Reposado and @vitafrute Blood Orange #VodkaSoda deserves its own literal/figurative pedestal. YES CORRECT: we bubbled up that beautiful #tequila with a canned vodka soda AND IT IS GLORIOUS. Also glorious: bright summer fruit syrup and the freshest egg whites (thank you for your service, Parsnip, but QUIT JUDGING ME WITH YOUR TINY, CUTE, JUDGEY CHICKEN FACE).
Link to recipe in bio.
